62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.600000381469727px; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><fieldset class=\"brcolor\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; BORDER-TOP: rgb(192,80,77) 1px dotted; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; BORDER-RIGHT: rgb(192,80,77) 1px dotted; BORDER-BOTTOM: rgb(192,80,77) 1px dotted; PADDING-BOTTOM: 20px; PADDING-TOP: 20px; PADDING-LEFT: 20px; MIN-HEIGHT: 1.5em; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(192,80,77) 1px dotted; LINE-HEIGHT: 2em; PADDING-RIGHT: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 15px; border-bottom-left-radius: 10px\"><legend style=\"max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; padding: 0px; text-align: center; margin: 0px; word-wrap: break-word !important;border:none;\"><p class=\"bkcolor\" style=\"word-wrap: normal; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; word-break: normal; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px 20px 4px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; line-height: 2em; border-bottom-right-radius: 100%!important; border-bottom-left-radius: 100%!important; background-color: rgb(192, 80, 77);\"><strong class=\"ue_t\" style=\"MAX-WIDTH: 100%\">今日寒露</strong></p></legend><p style=\"word-wrap: normal; max-width: 100%; word-break: normal; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; min-height: 1.5em; line-height: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; \">古代把露作为天气转凉变冷的标志。白露节气“露凝而白”，至寒露时已是“露气寒冷，将凝结”为霜了。寒露后已是深秋，天气开始转冷。露水更多，气温更低。</span><br/><span class=\"ue_t\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; LINE-HEIGHT: 2em;margin:0;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; white-space: pre-wrap; \"><br style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \"/><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); \"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; white-space: pre-wrap; \"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); \"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \">寒露。是24节气中最早出现“寒”字的节气，</strong></span>是夏阳入土的最后阶段，之后寒霜雪（霜降、小大雪）节节紧扣，离立冬还有1个月。</p></fieldset><p><br/></p><blockquote class=\"brcolor\" style=\"WORD-WRAP: break-word; FONT-SIZE: 14px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; VERTICAL-ALIGN: baseline; PADDING-BOTTOM: 15px; PADDING-TOP: 15px; PADDING-LEFT: 25px; MARGIN: 0px; BORDER-LEFT: rgb(102,102,102) 10px solid; DISPLAY: block; LINE-HEIGHT: 24px; TOP: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 25px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(238,238,238);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 108, 9); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \">【深秋滋阴润五脏】木瓜银耳猪骨汤</strong></blockquote><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"><img src=\"http://weituibao.qiniudn.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20141013/1413191781863951.jpg!editor.jpg\" title=\"1413191359248960.jpg\" alt=\"0 (1).jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">主打的木瓜清心润肺、健胃益脾；银耳、百合这些材料就不多说了，一个秋冬都要吃的。</span><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); \"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \">喝一碗，秋燥鼻子冒火的感觉没了，那种怎么喝水都喝不透的感觉才真正消除。<span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \">木瓜含有丰富的木瓜酵素。经常熬夜的人应多吃木瓜</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); \">，弥补体内的酵素。或者用木瓜来做酵素也非常应季。</span></strong></span><br/></p><p><span style=\"font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); \"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); \"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; white-space: pre-wrap; \"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); \">做法：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; white-space: pre-wrap; \"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); \">1、把干货材料提前泡半小时，猪骨飞水，洗干净后把除木瓜外的所有材料放入汤煲内，加水大火煮开后转小火慢煲；</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; white-space: pre-wrap; \"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); \">2、1小时后，切木瓜，去皮去籽，我喜欢把靠近籽的那一层内膜也去掉，这样汤煲出来就没有木瓜的异味了。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; white-space: pre-wrap; \"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); \">3、木瓜放入，煲软后即可关火。这个汤甜甜的不适合放盐调味。可以备一碟生抽蘸猪骨吃。</span></p><p><br/></p><blockquote class=\"brcolor\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; padding: 15px 25px; margin: 0px; border-left-color: rgb(102, 102, 102); border-left-width: 10px; border-left-style: solid; line-height: 24px; top: 0px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); \"><strong style=\"color: rgb(227, 108, 9); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \">【丝瓜络除风湿痛风】</strong></blockquote><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; \"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; \"><img src=\"http://weituibao.qiniudn.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20141013/1413191782357258.jpg!editor.jpg\" title=\"1413191772363643.jpg\" alt=\"0 (2).jpg\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; white-space: pre-wrap; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; white-space: pre-wrap; \">深秋的老丝瓜起络了，家里有痛风病人的可以收一些丝瓜络来。丝瓜络与橘络一样，能通络脉。<strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); \">很多病邪躲在人体细微处，就像藏在角落里的灰尘，而橘络和丝瓜络擅长钻进这些细小的地方进行清扫。</span></strong>橘络偏于疏通络脉中的痰淤，而丝瓜络偏于清除络脉中的风湿。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; white-space: pre-wrap; \"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: Helvetica, 宋体; line-height: 28px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; white-space: pre-wrap; \"><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); \"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \">【给痛风患者的丝瓜络茶】</strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; font-size: 15.5555562973022px; color: rgb(227, 108, 9); \">有关节炎、痛风的人可用丝瓜络煮水来调理。</span>把丝瓜络洗净，冷水下锅煮1小时代茶饮即可，对痛风病人有很好的效果。这可不是黑暗料理哦！</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127); \"><strong style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.600000381469727px; white-space: pre-wrap; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; \">做法：</strong><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.600000381469727px; white-space: pre-wrap; \"> </span><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.600000381469727px; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127); \">1、净老鸭和瘦猪肉分别切成3cm见方的块。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: normal; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.600